[l] Die Hollaender legen in Sachen Zivisiliation-Zurueckdrehen mal wieder vor. Hier ist, wie mein Einsender das uebersetzt und beschreibt:Dutch municipalities get more means to expel "people causing disturbances, such as criminals and extremists" from certain areas. "In the new law, prospective renters need to prove they have no criminal record. […] Police can be asked to research people who may have caused disturbances if these have not yet led to a criminal record. […] This way the radicalisation of others can be prevented."Da weiss man, was man hat!Und im naechsten Schritt lassen wir einfach Kriminelle nie wieder aus dem Knast. Denn wenn die dann eh nirgendwo wohnen koennen, …
